(18, 86, 'The Inca Empire', 'the-inca-empire', '<p><img style="float: left;" src="images/libros/9.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Panamá 2009</p>\r\n<p>Reforzar el uso de un segundo idioma, y al mismo tiempo aprender de nuestra historia es sin duda una aventura divertida, creativa y sobre todo cultural. Descubrir como eran tratados los niños en el tiempo de los Incas, qué hacían los chasquis (mensajeros del imperio) o varios rituales son duda lecturas que nos permitirán aprender más de lo que somos, para así proyectarnos mejor con los demás.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><button class="btn btn-info" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#Formulario"> Comprar libro </button></p>\r\n<div id="Formulario" class="collapse">{loadformmaker 6}</div>', '', 1, 11, '2017-12-10 19:31:04', 888, '', '2017-12-10 20:58:16', 888, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-12-10 19:31:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"article_layout":"","show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","info_block_show_title":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_associations":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_page_title":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 6, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(19, 87, 'Adiós Abuela. Hola Mamá', 'adios-abuela-hola-mama', '<p><img style="float: left;" src="images/libros/10.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Valencia España 2008</p>\r\n<p>​Adiós Abuela hola mamá nos cuenta la vida de Camila, su infancia llena de primos, travesuras y el amor de su abuela y de cómo la aparición de su madre y un viaje a España son una experiencia no muy fácil de sobrellevar. La migración, las familias rotas, los encuentros y desencuentros son parte de esta historia que se ha repetido en muchos países, en muchos hogares y en corazones de miles de niños y niñas.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><button class="btn btn-info" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#Formulario"> Comprar libro </button></p>\r\n<div id="Formulario" class="collapse">{loadformmaker 6}</div>', '', 1, 11, '2017-12-10 19:31:43', 888, '', '2017-12-10 20:58:29', 888, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-12-10 19:31:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"article_layout":"","show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","info_block_show_title":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_associations":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_page_title":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 5, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0,