(20, 88, 'Maravillosas Fábulas', 'maravillosas-fabulas', '<p><img style="float: left;" src="images/libros/11.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Quito 2008</p>\r\n<p>Los primeros libros de un niño, son sin duda los que lo deben motivar ha hacer de la lectura un hábito y por qué no un juego, en el que se divierte ya la vez aprender. Maravillosas Fábulas tiene las mejores lecturas en su género además de entretenidas y creativas fichas de trabajo, que permiten a los niños y niñas descubrir un mensaje positivo en cada historia leída.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><button class="btn btn-info" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#Formulario"> Comprar libro </button></p>\r\n<div id="Formulario" class="collapse">{loadformmaker 6}</div>', '', 1, 11, '2017-12-10 19:32:21', 888, '', '2017-12-10 21:01:14', 888, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-12-10 19:32:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"article_layout":"","show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","info_block_show_title":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_associations":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_page_title":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 4, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(21, 89, 'Ecuador People and Places', 'ecuador-people-and-places', '<p><img style="float: left;" src="images/libros/12.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Quito 2008</p>\r\n<p>Conocer un país, es conocer su cultura, su gente, su forma de vivir y cuando se aprende un segundo idioma, que mejor que aprender a compartir lo que somos y quienes nos representan.</p>\r\n<p>People and places brinda a los lectores la posibilidad de aprender y reforzar el uso de un segundo idioma, y también nos da la oportunidad de saber más de aquellos ecuatorianos ilustres y de los lugares más hermosos de este ensueño de país, llamado Ecuador.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><button class="btn btn-info" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#Formulario"> Comprar libro </button></p>\r\n<div id="Formulario" class="collapse">{loadformmaker 6}</div>', '', 1, 11, '2017-12-10 19:32:55', 888, '', '2017-12-10 20:59:06', 888, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-12-10 19:32:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"article_layout":"","show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","info_block_show_title":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_associations":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_page_title":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 3, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"